title: British tourist missing after South Curl Curl beach swim identified as Glen Sanderson
text:
British tourist missing after South C... British tourist missing after South Curl Curl beach swim identified as Glen Sanderson Next Story Prev Story 7 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
Missing British backpacker Glen Sanderson only arrived in Australia a week ago and was clearly keen to spend as much time as possible on the beach. The 31-year-old's posts on social media are a collection of pictures that show his fondness for the beach - him laying on the sand at Freshwater, the Bondi Surf Life Saving Club, the water views of a mate's house.   The Age.
